data.description: New alley access townhouses adjacent to the greenway, featuring a trendy 3 story design with an insulated 2 car garage.  The open concept living space with it's hardwood floors and granite counters has an upscale feel.  Master suite has dual vanity, relaxing garden tub, walk in closet and balcony. Convenient to shopping, gym, restaurants and interstates but also walking distance to the lake and less than 30 minutes to downtown Nashville. *$4000 builder incentives for a limited time
